entry.title: Drone Attacks Target Russian Supply Lines Ahead of Ukraine's Expected Offensive
entry.content: Strikes inside Russia target military logistics hubs in an apparent effort to disrupt Moscow’s ability to supply its troops.

entry.title: Gun Group's Financial Dealings With Founder Spark State Probe
entry.content: The Second Amendment Foundation, a group involved in several lawsuits to expand gun rights, said the Washington state attorney general’s office has examined transactions involving its founder, Alan Gottlieb.
